Author: notracisthasblackcat
Text: Can you track your calorie intake and slowly increase until you find a maintenance and then stay with that for a while? That' what I do

Author: Ohlivvy
Text: Your body will adjust to the calories and I take you're giving it. I'm sure a lot of it is water weight. Just relax, I'm sure you'll be fine soon. I k ow it's hard but you need to trust your body.
